---
title: Piña Colada Waffles with Cashews & Lime plus Sweet Cream Cheese Drizzle & Orange Slices
description: This easy 15-minute breakfast is bursting with tropical flavors! You’ll toast Belgian waffles (the thick fluffy kind!), and top with a silky maple-crème fraîche drizzle and maple-sweetened pineapple with lime. Sprinkle with coconut, crunchy cashews, and lime zest, and serve with orange slices for an easy, breezy, beach-inspired breakfast treat.
